data.name: txtInfoCreateListener.Text
data.value: ‚Logging-Connectors‘ store read variable data to the file system or a SQL database for further use. Due to not included database provider this example just shows filesystem and SQL-Server connections.

data.name: lblConnectionMessage.Text
data.value: PLCCom supports all database connections that derive from DbConnection- Object. PLCCom been tested with: => Oracle => MS SQL-Server => MySQL => PostgresSQL => OdbcConnection => OleConnection => Firebird => SQLITE
